{
  "stem": "2133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [CLEARS THROAT] but [CLEARS THROAT] as I said that for some of the people who wasn't that comfortable, you know, it was a difficult life, also.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents was-- wasn't-- my-- my father, I seen him used to go to the temple, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Practically every day, and so I would call it that he was religious, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother observed all the Jewish tradition and the holidays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] We always looked forward to the holidays, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was something special, particularly Pesach when it came, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] It was-- it was very, very lovely, you know, when-- when-- when my mother made very special dinner for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was an [CLEARS THROAT] excellent cook, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was an [CLEARS THROAT] extremely good-- matter of fact, you would her today a gourmet cook.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When people used to pass by the house, the-- our home, and the window was open and she would cook, she says, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Herskovits, we have to come in, because the smell what you-- comes out of your kitchen is not an average kitchen smell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We wanted to see what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that many years, I shouldn't be like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was bar mitzvahed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very nice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a godfather who insisted that I should become bar mitzvahed, and she was-- he was a very well-respected Jewish man in the city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't have children, so they practically took to me like their own child, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they treated me like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- they insisted that they're going to make my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] And they-- they did make it, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They made the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
